OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHeatwave: Schools to close 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25For let children wear PE kit
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fto keep cool               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A number of schools are closing next   
OL,6, week and others are ditching uniforms, 
OL,7, as temperatures in parts of the UK are 
OL,8, predicted to hit 40C (104F).           
OL,10,FA national emergency has been declared 
OL,11,Fafter a red extreme heat warning was   
OL,12,Fissued for Monday and Tuesday.         
OL,14,FSchools are not being ordered to shut, 
OL,15,Fbut are being encouraged to take steps 
OL,16,Fto ensure pupils are safe.             
OL,18,FTeachers say schools will need to judge
OL,19,Fwhether or not to fully or partially   
OL,20,Fclose in some instances.               
